Recommends: toilet
Description: Personalized SSH welcome message (MOTD) generator
 Alohomora creates beautiful, personalized Message of the Day (MOTD)
 screens for SSH logins. Features include:
  - Custom ASCII art banner using FIGlet fonts
  - Configurable color schemes
  - Local weather display
  - System stats (uptime, disk, memory, CPU)
  - Docker container status
  - Harry Potter themed splash messages
 .
 On installation, an interactive setup wizard helps you configure
 your personalized MOTD with your name, location, and color preferences.
